      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo spent every afternoon in the local library because the silence helped him think.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 4.312
            },
            {
              "text": "One rainy day, he found a small, handwritten note inside a dusty old book.",
              "audioStart": 5.175,
              "audioEnd": 9.662
            },
            {
              "text": "The note was about the beauty of life, which made him feel less alone.",
              "audioStart": 10.525,
              "audioEnd": 14.125
            },
            {
              "text": "He decided to write a short reply on the same page before he left.",
              "audioStart": 14.988,
              "audioEnd": 18.663
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He returned the next day to see if anyone had read his message.",
              "audioStart": 19.525,
              "audioEnd": 22.725
            },
            {
              "text": "To his surprise, a new, neat response was waiting for him.",
              "audioStart": 23.587,
              "audioEnd": 27.137
            },
            {
              "text": "This became a secret game between the two strangers who shared their favorite stories.",
              "audioStart": 28,
              "audioEnd": 32.2
            },
            {
              "text": "They started to leave notes in different books throughout the library.",
              "audioStart": 33.062,
              "audioEnd": 36.062
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo became very curious about the identity of the person who wrote back to him.",
              "audioStart": 36.925,
              "audioEnd": 41.038
            },
            {
              "text": "He wondered if she was a student or perhaps a teacher at the school nearby.",
              "audioStart": 41.9,
              "audioEnd": 45.25
            },
            {
              "text": "She seemed to understand his thoughts better than anyone else he knew.",
              "audioStart": 46.112,
              "audioEnd": 49.188
            },
            {
              "text": "They had never met, but their connection through words felt very real and strong.",
              "audioStart": 50.05,
              "audioEnd": 54.112
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "One afternoon, Leo arrived at the library to find a new note in his favorite book.",
              "audioStart": 54.975,
              "audioEnd": 59.35
            },
            {
              "text": "It invited him to meet at the center table at four o'clock that day.",
              "audioStart": 60.212,
              "audioEnd": 63.788
            },
            {
              "text": "He felt nervous but excited as he walked toward the meeting place.",
              "audioStart": 64.65,
              "audioEnd": 68.125
            },
            {
              "text": "He saw a girl sitting there with a book in her hand, waiting for someone.",
              "audioStart": 68.987,
              "audioEnd": 72.55
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo approached the girl and asked if she was the one who wrote the notes.",
              "audioStart": 73.412,
              "audioEnd": 76.888
            },
            {
              "text": "She looked up with a kind smile and held out a piece of paper.",
              "audioStart": 77.75,
              "audioEnd": 80.812
            },
            {
              "text": "Her name was Maya, and she had also been looking for a friend who loved stories.",
              "audioStart": 81.675,
              "audioEnd": 85.888
            },
            {
              "text": "They spent the rest of the evening talking about the characters they both adored.",
              "audioStart": 86.75,
              "audioEnd": 90.4
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They realized that their love for books had brought them together in such a special way.",
              "audioStart": 91.263,
              "audioEnd": 95.375
            },
            {
              "text": "Since that day, they have continued to read and share their ideas together.",
              "audioStart": 96.237,
              "audioEnd": 100.075
            },
            {
              "text": "Their friendship grew into something much deeper as they learned more about each other.",
              "audioStart": 100.938,
              "audioEnd": 104.838
            },
            {
              "text": "The library became the place where their new life together started.",
              "audioStart": 105.7,
              "audioEnd": 108.9
            }
          ]
        }
